'''瑟曼·李·蒙森'''（{{lang-en|Thurman Lee Munson}}，{{bd|1947年|6月7日|1979年|8月2日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的捕手。職業生涯全效力於紐約洋基隊。他生涯一共入選7次明星賽、3次金手套獎、1次年度MVP。

蒙森在1968年大聯盟選秀於第一輪第四順位被洋基隊選走。1970年，他拿下美聯新人王。1976年，他被任命為紐約洋基隊的隊長，同年拿下美聯MVP。1977年至1978年，他率領洋基隊拿下世界大賽二連霸。

1979年8月，蒙森駕駛著自己的私人飛機準備在阿克倫-坎頓機場降落。不過飛機在降落時卻發生事故，在駕駛艙的蒙森當場窒息身亡，享年僅32歲。<ref name=mdipc>{{cite news |url=http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1979/08/03/page/73/article/munson-dies-in-plane-crash |work=Chicago Tribune |title=Munson dies in plane crash |date=1979-08-03 |page=1, sec. 5}}</ref><ref name=tbysmkipc>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Cw0wAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3091%2C2937686 |work=Toledo Blade |location=(Ohio) |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees' star Munson is killed in plane crash |date=1979-08-03 |page=1 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085126/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Cw0wAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3091%2C2937686 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=nlcloym>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7fdLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vu4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6923%2C1367178 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=(Spokane, Washington) |agency=Associated Press |title='New love' claims life of Yanks' Munson |date=1979-08-03 |page=33 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085131/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7fdLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vu4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6923%2C1367178 |dead-url=no }}</ref>兩天後，洋基隊宣布將蒙森的15號背號永久退休，<ref name=yofimt>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4epIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xIIMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3645%2C993234 |work=Youngstown Vindicator |location=(Ohio) |agency=Associated Press |title=Yankees, O's, fans in Munson tribute |last=Bock |first=Hal |date=1979-08-04 |page=13 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085136/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=4epIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xIIMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3645%2C993234 |dead-url=no }}</ref>並設置一塊匾額放在主場後方的紀念碑公園以茲紀念。
==職業生涯==
===1968年–1970年===
1968年大聯盟選秀，洋基隊在第一輪第四順位選進了蒙森。該年他在小聯盟繳出3成01的打擊率，外帶6轟與37分打點的成績。1969年8月8日，蒙森登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196908082.shtml|title=New York Yankees 5, Oakland A's 0|date=1969-08-08|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101130255/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196908082.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在初登板便敲出2支安打與1分打點。2天後，他敲出了大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196908100.shtml|title=New York Yankees 5, Oakland A's 1|date=1969-08-10|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103004631/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA196908100.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成56，並敲出1轟與9分打點。由於他在1969年的打席數未達新人標準，因此他在1970年仍具有新秀身分。

1969年，當時洋基隊由Jake Gibbs和Frank Fernández擔任捕手工作。不過洋基隊在1970年將Fernández交易到運動家。而獲得大量出賽機會的蒙森也以3成02的打擊率，外帶7轟與57分打點的成績拿下美聯新人王。
===1971年–1974年===
1971年，蒙森首度入選明星賽。不過他只在後面2局接替守備，並無打擊記錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS197107130.shtml|title=1971 All-Star Game|date=1971-07-13|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2018-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180103132021/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/ALS/ALS197107130.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年蒙森僅發生一次失誤，因此他的防守也獲得極高的評價。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL197106180.shtml|title=Baltimore Orioles 6, New York Yankees 4|date=1971-06-18|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218061717/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BAL/BAL197106180.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而蒙森和紅襪隊的捕手[[卡爾頓·費斯克|卡爾頓·費斯克]]在當時也有瑜亮情結，兩人也保持著亦敵亦友的關係。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedeadballera.com/MunsonFisk.html|title=The Munson/Fisk Rivalry|accessdate=2009-11-25|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309105448/http://www.thedeadballera.com/MunsonFisk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>1973年8月1日，蒙森想利用Gene Michael的短打從三壘盜回本壘。不過Michael短打失敗，而費斯克用手肘給了Michael一個拐子後準備接球觸殺蒙森。蒙森也毫不示弱地用力往費斯克撞下去，最後雙方板凳清空引發10分鐘的大亂鬥，兩位捕手最終也都遭到驅逐出場。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BOS/BOS197308010.shtml|title=Boston Red Sox 3, New York Yankees 2|date=1973-08-01|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819085847/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/BOS/BOS197308010.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1973年，蒙森拿下生涯首座金手套獎，而他之後也完成了金手套3連霸。這年他的打擊率突破3成，並敲出了20轟，且成功入選明星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS197407230.shtml|title=1974 All-Star Game|date=1974-07-23|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2017-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170716235759/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NLS/NLS197407230.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===1975年–1976年===
1975年6月24日，蒙森與金鶯隊投手Mike Torrez發生口角衝突。原因是Torrez在第一局就對蒙森丟出觸身球，蒙森回敬兩支安打後，第四次打擊又被Torrez丟出觸身球。後來主審警告投手不得再丟出觸身球或近身球，結果Torrez給了蒙森一個飛吻。雙方也一度引發板凳清空，不過沒有發生互毆事件。最後蒙森擊出滾地球出局。<ref>{{cite book|last=Iber|first=Jorge|page=138|title=Mike Torrez: A Baseball Biography|publisher=McFarland|location=Jefferson, NC|year=2016|isbn=978-0-7864-9632-7}}</ref>該年蒙森締造生涯新高的3成15打擊率，在美聯排名第三。1976年球季開打前，洋基隊破天荒地宣布蒙森將成為洋基隊的隊長。該年他的打擊率為3成02，並敲出17轟與105分打點。成功幫助洋基隊睽違12年重返世界大賽，不過最後洋基隊不敵大紅機器，被紅人隊以4比0橫掃。但是蒙森也在世界大賽連6打席敲出安打，追平世界大賽紀錄。

紅人隊的捕手[[強尼·班奇|強尼·班奇]]拿下世界大賽MVP，然而紅人隊總教練Sparky Anderson卻以「拿蒙森跟班奇相比是一種羞辱」，造成蒙森極度的不滿。<ref>''All Roads Lead to October'' (chapter 10) by Maury Allen, St. Martin's Press 2000 {{ISBN|0-312-26175-6}}</ref>
===1977年–1979年===
1977年，蒙森的打擊率為3成08，並打回100分打點。他也成為大聯盟史上第二位能連續3年達成3成以上打擊率與100分以上打點的捕手(第一位是[[比爾·狄奇|比爾·狄奇]])。這年洋基隊又打進世界大賽，並在世界大賽上以4勝2敗擊退道奇拿下冠軍。

1978年，洋基與皇家連續3年在美聯冠軍賽相遇。蒙森在第三戰球隊4比5落後的情況下，於第8局敲出逆轉2分砲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197810060.shtml|title=1978 American League Championship Series Game Three|date=1978-10-06|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102185050/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197810060.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>最後洋基隊又闖入世界大賽，一樣以4勝2敗擊退道奇拿下2連霸。

蒙森也成為繼[[強尼·班奇|強尼·班奇]]後，第一位拿下新人王、金手套獎、年度MVP與世界大賽冠軍的捕手。日後也只有巨人隊的[[巴斯特·波西|巴斯特·波西]]加入此行列。

1979年，洋基隊僅在美東拿下第四名，落後第一名的金鶯隊達11場勝差。這年蒙森的打擊率下滑至2成88，他也開始思考是否退休或是回到他家鄉的球隊—印地安人隊效力。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/08/catcher_thurman_munson_the_cap.html|title=Catcher Thurman Munson, The Captain, was heart and soul of the NY Yankees|date=2009-08-01|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2018-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628021316/https://www.nj.com/yankees/index.ssf/2009/08/catcher_thurman_munson_the_cap.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時正值7月中，洋基隊已落後金鶯隊14場勝差。<ref name=yvmjloop>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3upIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xIIMAAAAIBAJ&pg=2939%2C180514 |work=Youngstown Vindicator |location=(Ohio) |title=Major loop standings |date=1979-08-01 |page=33 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085329/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3upIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xIIMAAAAIBAJ&pg=2939%2C180514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
==逝世==
蒙森在休賽季也有開飛機的嗜好。而他曾購買一架Cessna Citation I噴射機作為他的私人交通工具。<ref name=mrspapfst>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Dg0wAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6912%2C4393970 |work=Toledo Blade |location=(Ohio) |last=Lauck |first=Dan |title=Munson relative says plane a problem from start |date=1979-08-06 |page=16 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085312/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Dg0wAAAAIBAJ&sjid=iAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6912%2C4393970 |dead-url=no }}</ref>1979年8月2日，他一如往常的駕駛私人飛機準備降落在俄亥俄州的阿克倫-坎頓機場。飛機上除了蒙森還有他的好友Jerry Anderson以及飛行指導Dave Hall。<ref name=mdipc/><ref name=tbysmkipc/><ref name="DN01">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/2009/08/02/2009-08-02_the_mourning_after_munsons_death.html|title=Jerry Narron recalls night he replaced Thurman Munson for Yankees|last=Brennan|first=Sean|date=2009-08-01|publisher=New York Daily News|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2009-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090909090208/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/2009/08/02/2009-08-02_the_mourning_after_munsons_death.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>下午3點40分，蒙森即將降落在機場的23號道路上。然而降落時，蒙森沒有開啟飛機的襟翼，造成飛機直接墜落。最後飛機一路滑行，滑行到19號道路上，<ref name=ntsbapr80>{{cite web |url=https://www.ntsb.gov/investigations/AccidentReports/Reports/AAR8002.pdf |publisher=National Transportation Safety Board |agency=(Aircraft Accident Report) |title=Thurman L Munson, Cessna Citation, 501 N15NY, August 2, 1979 |date=1980-04-16 |access-date=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2021-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318160500/https://www.ntsb.gov/investigations/AccidentReports/Reports/AAR8002.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsnet5.com/dpp/news/news_archives/video-vault-1979-akron-canton-airport-plane-crash-killed-thurman-munson|title=Video Vault: 1979 Akron-Canton Airport plane crash killed Thurman Munson|first=Tom Livingston|last=newsnet5.com|date=2012-08-02|publisher=|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019182932/http://www.newsnet5.com/dpp/news/news_archives/video-vault-1979-akron-canton-airport-plane-crash-killed-thurman-munson|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=tfyltrnydn>{{cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/thurman-munson-final-hours-article-1.394320 |work=New York Daily News |last=Coffey |first=Wayne |title=25 years later, Thurman Munson's last words remain a symbol of his life |agency=(originally from 2004) |date=2009-08-01 |accessdate=2018-06-27 |archive-date=2014-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104211222/http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/baseball/yankees/thurman-munson-final-hours-article-1.394320 |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後撞上樹墩後起火燃燒。<ref>''All Roads Lead to October'' (chapter 10) by Maury Allen, St. Martin's Press 2000 {{ISBN|0-312-26175-6}}, reprinted at {{cite web |url=http://www.thurmanmunson.com/history.html |title=last entry for the ThurmanMunson.com history page |accessdate=2007-02-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070202205405/http://www.thurmanmunson.com/history.html |archivedate=2007-02-02 }}</ref>

Anderson和Hall都成功地逃過一劫，不過兩人都有燒燙傷。而蒙森最後沒有成功逃出來，由於飛機被撞到變形，蒙森的駕駛座整個被機身卡死。最終蒙森因高溫窒息而去世。後來發現蒙森因為高度力道的撞擊而造成頸椎骨折，這也是造成他無法成功逃生的原因之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=md4iAAAAIBAJ&sjid=48sFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3234,3052035&dq=thurman+munson+cause+of+death&hl=en |title=Coroner: Paralyzed Munson couldn't escape|publisher=}}</ref>

這起意外造成美國的[[國家運輸安全委員會|國家運輸安全委員會]]新增了蒙森條款：規定12500磅以上的飛機不得由一人操控駕駛。

==紀念==
[[File:ThurmanMunson15.jpg|thumb]]
蒙森去世後，洋基隊在賽前舉辦了追思儀式。並宣布將蒙森的15號背號永久退休。洋基隊讓年僅23歲的Jerry Narron擔任先發捕手，而他也在追思儀式中坐在板凳上，以紀念長期擔任洋基捕手的蒙森。

8月6日，洋基隊的所有成員都參加了蒙森的葬禮。並由蒙森以前的好友[[盧·皮涅拉|盧·皮涅拉]]和Bobby Murcer念出悼詞。<ref name=mnsneulg>{{cite news |url=http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1979/08/07/page/39/article/munson-eulogized-by-yankee-teammates |work=Chicago Tribune |title=Munson eulogized by Yankee teammates |date=1979-08-07 |page=1, sec.4}}</ref><ref name=msahaf>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8fdLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vu4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6533%2C4114127 |work=Spokesman-Review |location=(Spokane, Washington) |agency=Associated Press |title=Munson's son a hit at funeral |date=1979-08-07 |page=19 |accessdate=2020-11-08 |archive-date=2022-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220109085437/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8fdLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=vu4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6533%2C4114127 |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來Murcer也在比賽中打回5分打點，包含一發3分砲，洋基最終以5比4贏球。<ref name=cteul>{{cite news |url=http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1979/08/07/page/39/article/murcer-delivers-a-tribute|work=Chicago Tribune |title=Murcer delivers a tribute |date=1979-08-07 |page=1, sec.4}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197908060.shtml|title=New York Yankees 5, Baltimore Orioles 4|date=1979-08-06|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2020-11-08|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125021933/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/NYA/NYA197908060.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>1980年9月26日，洋基隊在紀念碑公園設置了一座蒙森的紀念匾額。洋基隊老闆[[喬治·史坦布瑞納|喬治·史坦布瑞納]]也親自題字：
{{quote|Our captain and leader has not left us, today, tomorrow, this year, next ... Our endeavors will reflect our love and admiration for him.<br/>(我們的隊長和領導人沒有離開我們，今天、明天、今年、下次......我們的努力將反映出我們對他的愛和欽佩。)}}

==家庭==
